commit.title: Extract the record encoding information out of the kernel.
commit.message:
Extract the record encoding information out of the kernel.

Instead, we remember that an inductive stands for the encoding of a record
in a table in Recordops. This allows to simplify both the kernel and the
upper layers. In the process it makes clear who is depending on this data.
